import React from 'react'
import {Container,Row,Col} from 'react-bootstrap';


function Body() {
  return (
    <>
     <Container>
         <Row>
             <Col md={2}>sd
             </Col>
             <Col>dsd</Col>
             <Col>sd</Col>
             <Col>sd</Col>
         </Row>
     </Container>
    </>
  )
}

export default Body
